<br>
I remember &quot;zone wars&quot; and the such, where you cant have fun or go to zones that you want to, because there are &quot;land disputes&quot; and evils can only play in one place, and good can only play in another.<br>
<br>
In essence, EQ PVP is terrible.  There is no balance, casters seem to have the low end.  All i saw on the sullen zek board was a bunch of &quot;OMG, U R GEY AND FAG! OMG LOLOL U R SUX&quot; attitudes.  I will never go back.<br>
<br>
